<!--<h4>First side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>svasti śrī</unclear> naviluguṁdada śrī jvāḷāmāḷinīdēviya basadiya śrīkāryyakke <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> malladēvaṁ sarbbanamaśyavāgi biṭṭa jāvūranuṁ śrī sakaḷacaṁdra bhaṭṭārakadēvarige <unclear>punarddharmma</unclear>
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <unclear>ri</unclear>ya māḍi bīciseṭṭi sarvvanamaśyavāgi koṭṭa jāvūranallā Arasugaḷu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>hadineṁṭu samayaṁgaḷu pālisuvarāsthaḷadācāryaru śrījayakīrtti dēvaru māḍisida <unclear>śi</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> <note n="408-1">The continuation is</note>
</p>

<!--<h4>Second side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmatu
<lb n="2"/>naviluguṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dada jvāḷinīdē
<lb n="4" break="no"/>viya basadi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ya haḷi
</p>

